beer.beer_description: The beer was inspired by our recent trip to San Diego where we lived entirely on a diet of fish tacos and craft beer! It's a hoppy Ale brewed with coriander leaf, fresh lime peel and corn. It's fresh, zesty and dangerously drinkable. And of course, is the perfect pairing for tacos!
